reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best Customer Service to Date
reviews.reviewText: I got this vacuum as a replacement for a previous version that I bought a year ago. I reached out to the company expecting to get info for where to purchase a new batter and they did me one better. They advised me to purchase a newer model and REFUNDED ME for my previous purchase! It was above and beyond anything I expected when I reached out.The vacuum itself works well. I like that it has 3 settings and digitally tells me how much I have left in the charge. The 3rd setting works wonders on my thicker carpet and the first is great for my hardwood floors. I had to empty it multiple times when I vacuumed because it picked up a good amount of stuff off of my floor.
